\par \tab \loch\af0\dbch\af12\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 You go.\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Haelin quietly moved to the horses. \'93\loch\f0 Try\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0  to book passage for three, but don\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 t wait for me. I\hich\f0 
