\par \tab \loch\af0\dbch\af12\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 And you will do what?\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Kell asked. \'93\loch\f0 Will you cut their throats? That is u\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
nlike you. You know that you could not stand against them all. On your best day, I would not lay coin on you against three, and you are now wounded.\'94
\par \tab \loch\af0\dbch\af12\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Like you said, she needs somewhere safe to recover.\'94\loch\f0  Haelin put the gold into Kell\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s hand. \'93\loch\f0 You have to \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 
