\par \tab \loch\af0\dbch\af12\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 The odds are three to one,\'94\loch\f0  Haelin said.
\par \tab \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Horst drew his sword. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 You must really want to die.\'94
\par \tab \loch\af0\dbch\af12\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Not really,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Haelin said. \'93\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 \hich\f0 But for once in my life, I have a good reason to do so.\'94
\par \tab \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 The last two men also drew their swords, but they didn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 t move.
\par \tab \loch\af0\dbch\af12\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 Kell said that I couldn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t beat three of you on my best day.\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Haelin drew sword and dirk. \'93\loch\f0 Let\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 
