\par \tab \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 Luckily f\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 or Haelin, two of them had all the finesse of said smith.
\par \tab \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 Haelin concentrated on Horst. He was the threat. Any opportunity he offered stank of a trap. Any lethargy in his arm screamed deception. Haelin focused his defenses on Horst while seeking an openin
\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 g with either of the other two. He had to move, keep aware of the stable around him, of the implements, the straw, the stalls and the walls.
