\par \tab \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 One of Horst\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s men stumbled. Haelin opened up his th\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 roat then danced back from Horst\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s thrust.
