\par \tab \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 His exhaustion was only partly a feint. Whatever magic the girl could call upon, it could not heal completely. Haelin could sense the weak\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 
ness in his arm returning. He had taxed the strength in his body, and it had little more to offer.
\par \tab \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 Horst and his man attacked with both fury and desperation. Haelin noted that Horst\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s style had changed, if only slightly. Horst no longer had the confidence\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 
 that made him dangerous. He hesitated in his attacks. Doubts slowed him, made him question himself. That gave Haelin the edge he needed. Sliding away from Horst\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s man\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
