\par \tab \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Haelin glanced at the three bodies. \'93\loch\f0 In all honesty, you are welcome to try. I\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 m not going to kill you because you spared the girl last night. That debt\hich\f0 \rquote 
